		<title>Old Spice zeigt was mit Social Media geht</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/01Podcast/~3/1TUijZO6tBk/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.cebit.de/2010/07/14/old-spice-zeigt-was-mit-social-media-geht/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 14 Jul 2010 14:25:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>timpritlove@gmail.com (Tim Pritlove &amp; Max Winde)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Marketing & E-Commerce 2.0]]></category>
